Summary: Verify that the word length exceeding the comment section of the post will print in different lines or not
Creator: Anamika
Description:
Steps to the issue: 
1. Navigate to Elearning application
2. Click and sign up and enter the valid credentials
3. Go to Social network and Choose My Shared Profile
4. Verify that the word length exceeding the comment section of the post will print in different lines or not

Expected Result:
If the length of a word is exceeding the layout size of comment box then it will be printed in the next line on wards.

Actual Result:
If the length of a word is exceeding the layout size of the comment box then it still printing it in the same line.

Test Data:
asuhfguhfdggdsugfdsuhgfsduhgsfduhfdgsuhfsdgushfdgfsduhgfdsuhgfduhfguhfsguhfsguhfguhfsdguhfsgufsgufsdgusfgufgs

*Actual Result:*
